    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"liberating\" is a heavy word to use. you make it sound like there's some kind of relief in being broken beyond repair. i just feel tired. tired of being this... this leftover thing that doesn't belong in the world anymore. if the person i was is truly gone, then what's the point of keeping the rest of this around?",
